      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The engine performs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor signs of normal wear consistent with its age. It is a dependable, turn-key vehicle that is ready for daily use or long-distance travel.",
