      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly such a great find. It's been really well-loved and is in solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it for your next adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
