    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 straight-six engine, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed RTABs, ensuring the suspension geometry remains precise under lateral load. Riding on staggered Style 67 alloys, this example maintains a taut, communicative steering rack and a linear power band that pulls strongly to the 8,000 RPM redline. While showing honest patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the mechanical vitals are robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
